Editor v0.3 beta
#####################


liste de commandes 

ctrl + a:to switch
clear    							 // to clear the screen
open [namefile] 				     //open a file
save [namefile]  					 // save a file
new   								 // to create a new buffer
buffer+  							 // go to the next buffer
buffer- 							 // go to the previous buffer

// pour changer la coloration juste taper le nom de langage


to compile just type ./start.sh

